title: Florence Schelling, Jennie-Lee Burmansson, and the last day of Lausanne 2020
description: Swiss ice hockey goaltender Florence Schelling gave her advice on how to survive the tough times. Swedish freeskier Jennie-Lee Burmansson talks what makes her sport so special. And we have a last question about Johnny Depp.
